nks about his life in terms of making content for Twitter.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Is that a good sign for his reign as Chief Twi=
t? Oh, who knows, probably not; my other theory about Twitter is that it=E2=
=80=99s probably for the best that no one who works there uses the product.=
